Link in bio!!

Just landed back in LA and I’m still excited about my team winning our backyard olympics! My saving grace from this past weekend to have fun in the sun and protect my skin in the Hamptons was @bondisands Fragrance Free SPF 50 Body Sunscreen! You guys know this is my jam. Cruelty free, doesn’t leave you greasy after using it, and gives you a nice dewy glow! 
-
Use code ‘SAMI’ to get 20% off at bondisands.com! #bondisandssuncare

Time to head home and pack a new bag!! Getting ready for lots of travels this month which means finding the time and the place to move my body. Next stop NYC! Wearing my @reebok Nano X1 Adventure’s makes it so easy - love wearing them on my walks or in my workouts!! #NanoXAadventure #reebokpartner 
-
What’s your favorite type of movement while on travels??

node.text:
It would only be natural for me to find a mirror, take a mirror pic, while in Cabo, wearing the @itsherown bikini!!! 
-
Could not be more proud of @helenowen for putting her heart into this line & now being able to shoot it with @modelistemagazine @garzablancaloscabos !!
-
Cheers to friends chasing their dreams and getting to support one another! Can’t wait to see how the photos from today turn out! #modearoundglobe #garzablancaloscabos #itsherown
